	<title>dialogKit: Coordinates</title>
	
	<include src="settings/main.xml" />
	
	<div class="content">
	    
	    <div class="sectionName">
	       Coordinates
	    </div>
	    
	    <div class="sectionDescription">
	       
	        <p>
                All of the dialogKit objects require a posSize argument during initialization. The passed data should be a tuple of the form <b>(left, top, width, height)</b> <i>except</i> in the case of ModalDialog. That object will accept a tuple of the form <b>(width, height)</b> as well as the standard form. The top left corner of the dialog (excluding the menu bar) is position 0, 0.
	        </p>
	        
